---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 289
  - Title: Yoga-Vasishtha
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Orthodoxy-Ritual-Method=The Spiritual Master
  - 85
Glossary:
  - Term: Shastras
    Definition: The Hindu scriptures
---
The mistaken impression of the reality of the world is never to be
effaced without the knowledge of its unreality derived from the
Shastras, and the living lips of a Teacher.
